data.value:
Generic name: Meclizine HCI Dosage: 25mg chewable tablet Use: Anti-emetic; Anti-vertigo Indication of use: Adults and children above 11 yrs old: [Motion sickness] Take 1-2 tablets one hour before travel for 24-hr protection. [Nausea and vomiting] Take 1-2 tablets per day
Product is sold per blister pack
